platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: ClassDojo offers teachers a wonderful way to manage their classroom using an iPad or iPhone. With the app’s extremely simple interface, tracking attendance and recording students’ behavior is a snap, and ClassDojo produces helpful reports instructors can share with parents and colleagues.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Manage your classroom and easily share reports with parents and colleagues.
